description:
Here it is… a cleansing lifestyle re-boot that will help to shift elements from all aspects of your life which may no longer be serving you. It’s a simple program for busy people living busy lives that I’ve created to help you live your most nourished life.

My Cleansed eBook will educate, motivate, inspire, nourish and balance your body, mind and spirit.

Get ready to improve your health, your flow, your rhythm, your energy and your life. 

Ready? 

Go.

name: Gluten Free Meal Plan
description:
Going gluten free? Let me help. 

Purchase my healthy, naturopathic and nutritionally-balanced meal plan and you'll receive:

~ A 7-day eating plan loaded with delicious, nutritious meals and snacks – and I promise, you won’t go hungry!
~ A food diary so you can log your progress
~ Essential tips and tricks to keep you on track with your desired health goals

I know you can't wait to get started, so once purchased, you'll be emailed a link to instantly download your meal plan. You'll be able to use the download link 3 times, so make sure you save your meal plan to your computer or iBook library. 


Big thanks, hugs & mugs of chai,

Cass x

name: Business Development & Mentoring
description:
Starting out in clinic can be tough, no matter how many clinic hours you completed in college. I've been there, and I know how important it is to find a mentor who can guide you through the first few stages of starting your practice, running a business and building your client base. 

Mentoring sessions run for 1 hour and can be claimed for CPE points as well as for tax purposes (price includes GST).

Bring a notepad, some questions, and lets smooth away the nerves of starting out. 

Once purchased, please call reception on (02) 8968 9326 to book your mentoring session. 

Cass x

name: Elevate Your Vitality - Webinar Recording
description:
This hugely popular event gives you simple, practical and accessible ways to improve your health & wellbeing, from me, a passionate & dedicated naturopath.

Here's what people are saying:

"Thanks for a fantastic night! Your presentation style was relaxed and easy to listen to. It was also a wonderful opportunity to connect with like-minded people and ask you questions. You covered a lot of ground, I look forward to the next one. Much love xx" - Francine

"Thank you SO much for the webinar! Was very insightful and packed full of great info highly recommend to anyone who is either just starting on their path to wellness or well on the path.. Full of good stuff for everyone." - Melissa

"What a beautiful way to kick-start the week with your amazing webinar!! I loved the way you so brilliantly combined easy to understand information on nourishing the mind + body + soul by sharing actionable tips and knowledge on nutrition and herbal medicine - well done Cass, can't wait for your next one! Xx" - Cara

name: Self Love & Nourishment e-course
description: Self-Love & Nourishment is a 6-week e-course designed to help foster and nurture teens and women’s sense of self love, self compassion and self-esteem, while also promoting optimal mental, emotional, spiritual and physical wellness. It’s the first of its kind in Australia, having been written and created by two experienced and passionate wellness practitioners - kinesiologist and life coach, Clare Woodward, and naturopath, nutritionist and herbalist, Cassie Mendoza-Jones. The first round brought women together from 5 different countries around the globe! Round 2 launches early 2014! To register your interest for Round 2, and receive a FREE nourishing meal plan, click here. To your self love & nourishment, Cass & Clare x P.S. Come visit us on Facebook
